News.Title: Felix Industries Secures Order Worth 325.7 Million Rupees
News.Summary: Felix Industries has announced that it has received an order valued at 325.7 million rupees. This significant contract represents a positive development for the company's business operations and potential revenue growth.

News.Title: Felix Industries to Acquire 20% Stake in Eco-vision Aqua Care
News.Summary: Felix Industries has announced plans to acquire a 20% stake in Eco-vision Aqua Care for 42 million rupees. This strategic investment represents a significant corporate action for Felix Industries, potentially expanding its presence in the water treatment sector.
